00:56:54.460 --> 00:56:57.460
Mali is located in Western Africa,

00:56:57.460 --> 00:57:00.460
reaching well into the Sahara Desert.

00:57:00.460 --> 00:57:03.460
The northern part of the country is hot and covered with sand,

00:57:03.460 --> 00:57:05.460
but the southern region,

00:57:05.460 --> 00:57:07.460
which is watered by the Niger River,

00:57:07.460 --> 00:57:11.460
is green with forests and vegetation.

00:57:11.460 --> 00:57:14.460
The witnesses in the country have a huge task,

00:57:14.460 --> 00:57:17.460
as the ratio of Jehovah's Witnesses to population

00:57:17.460 --> 00:57:22.460
is about one publisher to 59,000 residents.

00:57:22.460 --> 00:57:25.460
Also, the distances are tremendous.

00:57:25.460 --> 00:57:29.460
The approximately 300 publishers cover an area

00:57:29.460 --> 00:57:33.460
more than twice the size of the country of France.

00:57:33.460 --> 00:57:36.460
Mali is one of the hottest countries in the world,

00:57:36.460 --> 00:57:40.460
so some groups and congregations hold their meetings outdoors,

00:57:40.460 --> 00:57:43.460
under the cool shade of a tree.

00:57:43.460 --> 00:57:47.460
Although the official language of the country is French,

00:57:47.460 --> 00:57:51.460
most people better understand the local language, Bambara.

00:57:51.460 --> 00:57:56.460
Thus, most meetings are either held or interpreted in Bambara.

00:57:56.460 --> 00:57:59.460
Recently, language classes were held in Beaumont,

00:57:59.460 --> 00:58:02.460
which is another local language.

00:58:02.460 --> 00:58:06.460
Also, the seven publishers of the American Sign Language Week

00:58:06.460 --> 00:58:11.460
have been assigned to witness to the more than 350,000 people

00:58:11.460 --> 00:58:14.460
in Mali who have a hearing impairment.

00:58:14.460 --> 00:58:17.460
Last year, the total attendance for the memorial

00:58:17.460 --> 00:58:20.460
was over 1,100 people.

00:58:20.460 --> 00:58:24.460
One man who received an invitation walked three kilometers,

00:58:24.460 --> 00:58:27.460
or almost two miles to attend the memorial,

00:58:27.460 --> 00:58:31.460
despite having a physical challenge with his foot.

00:58:31.460 --> 00:58:33.460
He is now regular at the meetings

00:58:33.460 --> 00:58:36.460
and is making good progress.

